{"tid":1129432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★股災？】公司車涉繞道逆線行　前藝人吳啟明認錯：新聘司機唔識路","createTime":"2019-04-28T12:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T06:35:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a863d845eb9f0aafe9bb96db2661e3b6c954452","tid":1129432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190428194302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190428194302&h=007c9200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳啟明(左)在電視劇《大時代》飾演「丁旺蟹」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190428194302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190428194302&h=b4866e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一部掛有中港車牌的私家車昨晚(27日)疑於中環及灣仔繞道逆線行駛，相關片段在網上流傳引起公眾嘩然，警方暫列「危險駕駛」處理，呼籲目擊者提供資料。東網接獲消息指，涉事車輛後座一位乘客為前藝人吳啟明。吳接受東網訪問時承認，昨晚原定前往中環四季酒店參加圈外朋友舉辦的宴會，未料涉事司機突然逆線駛入繞道，「嚇到我面都青晒」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=3b95a1b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"60a495c54872cda0eec8110d8f918902eae4b0f4","tid":1129432,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"丁蟹效應下周殺到！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1126656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1126656</a><br />\